description:
Welcome to our peaceful, spacious villa in West Bay, home to a warm, mostly European expat community. Just a 10-minute walk to City Center Doha and steps from a local mini-market, bakery, pharmacy, dry cleaner, park, and more – convenience is all around. 
Room Details:
Fully furnished room available now – large bed, desk, sofa, TV. QAR 4000/month, all bills included (electricity, water, internet, Ooredoo TV, StarzPlay Being Sport,). Window AC included. 
House Features:
• Fully equipped kitchen & upstairs kitchenette
• Two cozy living rooms
• Courtyard with covered seating
• Beautiful Garden + roof terrace (both great for BBQs)
• High-speed broadband
• Laundry room with washer
• Ample Street parking
About Us:
We’re a laid-back, friendly group who enjoy BBQs and occasional get-togethers. The villa has rustic charm and may need occasional maintenance – perfect for someone easygoing who appreciates character over luxury. 
Details:
• Minimum stay: 6 months
• Deposit: 1 month’s rent
• Western expats preferred (others welcome)
• Cat lovers only – we have two
• Outdoor smoking only
• Shorter stays are negotiable at a higher rate
• No families, please
